{"tid":857500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話叫人上去住大灣區，填乜野海姐。","createTime":"2018-10-11T06:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T05:24:50.000Z","uid":156363,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25f5bfb442e465ffa0eeeb1052a7f7eb27f4149d","tid":857500,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"唐唐果個年代深圳4號線未通車就叫人搬去龍崗，林鄭西九就黎通車就叫人上大灣區住。<br />\n<br />\n叫香港人搬晒上去咪得囉，仲填乜野海姐？填俾邊個住啊？有一萬億不如補貼下條高鐵啦。"},{"pid":"4c105390248bc0b00e537aa9de8c8936abf3082a","tid":857500,"uid":77556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"填出黎係俾你地班香港人住架咩？<br />\n你地班香港人就繼續返大灣區住<br />\n嗰班大陸新移民咪有位落黎香港新地住囉"},{"pid":"4c3243450fedf815e50f234aed8e8a50aa28fbf6","tid":857500,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}